[Amit Varma]: aspects of the pandemic that I've noted one the smaller one almost a trivial one

00:09:17.280 --> 00:09:22.000
[Amit Varma]: that I chatted about with Anup Malani in the episode I did with him is that it

00:09:22.000 --> 00:09:26.000
[Amit Varma]: inverted some of our values like some of the things which could otherwise be

00:09:26.000 --> 00:09:30.120
[Amit Varma]: considered good suddenly worked against us like population density which we know

00:09:30.120 --> 00:09:33.520
