00:09:33.520 --> 00:09:37.240
[Amit Varma]: people together more opportunities all of that but in the context of this

00:09:37.240 --> 00:09:43.200
[Amit Varma]: pandemic that suddenly you know became a bit of a con but that's a trivial minor

00:09:43.200 --> 00:09:46.960
[Amit Varma]: thing the larger thing that I noticed and I wrote a column about it last year

00:09:46.960 --> 00:09:51.640
[Amit Varma]: in April when this first began stating that our greater crisis is not just

00:09:51.640 --> 00:09:57.040
[Amit Varma]: COVID which will pass but the dysfunctional Indian state which has been in crisis

00:09:57.040 --> 00:10:01.480
[Amit Varma]: for you know the last 70 years I think in that column I used to start I don't

00:10:01.480 --> 00:10:04.440
[Amit Varma]: really remember it but something like 3,000 children in India die of

00:10:04.440 --> 00:10:07.680
[Amit Varma]: starvation every day something like that I'm sure you have kind of better stats

00:10:07.680 --> 00:10:11.120
[Amit Varma]: which to me is indicative of an ongoing disaster which we have completely

00:10:11.120 --> 00:10:15.600
[Amit Varma]: normalized and if there's one thing that COVID has done it has shed light on a

00:10:15.600 --> 00:10:19.840
[Amit Varma]: lot of things which we had normalized the apathy of politicians the

00:10:19.840 --> 00:10:24.060
[Amit Varma]: dysfunctional state more than anything else the fact that the state simply

00:10:24.060 --> 00:10:28.800
[Amit Varma]: doesn't work I mean I've always said that where the state is most required

00:10:28.800 --> 00:10:33.000
[Amit Varma]: most justified it is absent there is effectively no rule of law in India and

00:10:33.000 --> 00:10:37.760
[Amit Varma]: today we see that in the state of our healthcare where it was most required it

00:10:37.760 --> 00:10:42.360
[Amit Varma]: was absent and we are see kind of seeing the consequences of that so do you think

00:10:42.360 --> 00:10:46.840
[Amit Varma]: that there is also therefore a teachable moment in this that you can look at this

00:10:46.840 --> 00:10:52.000
[Amit Varma]: moment and say that listen these things have been wrong forever right we haven't

00:10:52.000 --> 00:10:55.440
[Amit Varma]: noticed them right now you are all looking at them because they are stuck

