[Amit Varma]: and and there is a will to do that and then think about what to do is this

00:11:10.120 --> 00:11:14.080
[Amit Varma]: something that you've thought about and as someone who studied the inner workings

00:11:14.080 --> 00:11:19.400
[Amit Varma]: of both the state and healthcare so deeply for so many years you know is

