[Amit Varma]: positive externalities if everyone is healthy are so huge that of course the

00:17:40.160 --> 00:17:43.960
[Amit Varma]: state has to do it especially in a poor country like India but if the problem is

00:17:43.960 --> 00:17:47.840
[Amit Varma]: not getting solved from there then private people have to step in and find

00:17:47.840 --> 00:17:52.880
[Amit Varma]: ways to do it what are your thoughts on this I'm sorry if I rambled a bit

