[Amit Varma]: the other interesting aspect which is that does teaching teach you in the sense

00:24:31.760 --> 00:24:35.800
[Amit Varma]: that if you think about there being like I think in an earlier episode with me

00:24:35.800 --> 00:24:39.400
[Amit Varma]: Krish Ashok had spoken about this pyramid of learning where you know your

00:24:39.400 --> 00:24:42.440
[Amit Varma]: learning is more shallow if you just listen to something it's a little deeper

00:24:42.440 --> 00:24:46.840
[Amit Varma]: if you read it and so on down the way and it's deepest if you teach it I think

00:24:46.840 --> 00:24:50.420
[Amit Varma]: so in your case you mentioned that one of the ways you workshop the book was

00:24:50.420 --> 00:24:54.120
[Amit Varma]: you also taught bits of it did the process of teaching it having to pare

00:24:54.120 --> 00:24:57.840
[Amit Varma]: everything down to a systematic structure explain it in simple language

00:24:57.840 --> 00:25:02.640
[Amit Varma]: answer questions on it did that deepen your understanding and in general does

00:25:02.640 --> 00:25:05.960
[Amit Varma]: you know through your career you've obviously been an incredible

00:25:05.960 --> 00:25:10.760
[Amit Varma]: researcher that's a matter of public record but you've also taught so what's

00:25:10.760 --> 00:25:15.880
[Amit Varma]: the relationship there between teaching and learning there's a reason why top

00:25:15.880 --> 00:25:19.640
[Guest]: research universities have this positive feedback loop between research and

00:25:19.640 --> 00:25:23.320
[Guest]: teaching right so there's no question about it that the act of putting

00:25:23.320 --> 00:25:26.920
[Guest]: together a lecture and teaching forces you to distill both what you want your

00:25:26.920 --> 00:25:30.600
[Guest]: audience to understand and how do we know what we know I'm forgetting his

00:25:30.600 --> 00:25:33.800
[Guest]: name now because his handle is Bhalo Manush right but like you know four

00:25:33.800 --> 00:25:39.080
[Guest]: episodes but what Anirban mentioned right like you know that when he got to

