[Guest]: to be a tradition where health was left to doctors and education was left to

00:35:46.160 --> 00:35:50.920
[Guest]: educators but policy is fundamentally about allocating scarce resources and so

00:35:50.920 --> 00:35:54.920
[Guest]: you kind of need an economic lens in this right so the public finance aspects

00:35:54.920 --> 00:35:59.520
[Guest]: of why healthcare is you know occupies a large share of my mind space is a that

