00:57:20.440 --> 00:57:24.480
[Guest]: economics of national security okay so an even bigger black box of public

00:57:24.480 --> 00:57:29.280
[Guest]: funding is what we spend on defense okay so one very very very simple metric of

00:57:29.280 --> 00:57:33.320
