[Guest]: qualified doctor to be able to cater to larger populations so now the question

02:43:50.240 --> 02:43:53.080
[Guest]: is when we look at the infrastructure budget the health ministry is not even

02:43:53.080 --> 02:43:57.640
[Guest]: thinking about this right so at the very least what I would like is to a finance

