02:44:00.800 --> 02:44:04.360
[Guest]: the health benefits or something like this and you know and therefore put

02:44:04.360 --> 02:44:07.280
[Guest]: correspondingly more money in some of those broader public goods that will

02:44:07.280 --> 02:44:10.720
[Guest]: have higher return so that's one principle okay a public goods now the

