[Amit Varma]: alcohol so the guy won't go and beat up his wife secondly I think you think of

02:44:36.200 --> 02:44:39.280
[Amit Varma]: it only as something that emits carbon and pollutes the air and is bad for

02:44:39.280 --> 02:44:42.760
[Amit Varma]: health is a problem because I think the positive externalities are far greater

