[Guest]: think you guys had the same back and forth right where Ashwin was talking

02:47:03.320 --> 02:47:06.080
[Guest]: about you know what we need to do to take back the government right I mean so

02:47:06.080 --> 02:47:10.400
[Amit Varma]: there is no no I I agree with that aspect of it my my problem here is that

