[Amit Varma]: utopian argument that the you know that it will be okay to tax patrol more more

02:47:20.480 --> 02:47:25.240
[Amit Varma]: if the state can do all of these things the state is not doing any of those

02:47:25.240 --> 02:47:27.840
[Amit Varma]: things and the other point I want to make is that when you talk about the

02:47:27.840 --> 02:47:31.640
[Amit Varma]: India plane and the rich can buy private goods and all of that the point is roads

02:47:31.640 --> 02:47:35.640
[Amit Varma]: are good for everyone including the poor and I would argue that keeping petrol

