[Guest]: government do with any amount of money okay the second is saying that that we

02:47:48.360 --> 02:47:53.440
[Guest]: want the government to make certain core investments right means so suppose there

02:47:53.440 --> 02:47:57.560
[Guest]: is a menu of investments post COVID right that we say these are clearly high

02:47:57.560 --> 02:48:03.200
[Guest]: return public investments okay now there is always a possibility of saying we

02:48:03.200 --> 02:48:07.280
[Guest]: will not raise taxes let's cut down all of our inefficient spending okay and

02:48:07.280 --> 02:48:10.400
[Guest]: then move it to the more efficient ones okay which would be my preferred outcome

